| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5123 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fae062eb-fcaa-5986-bfd6-c5c6d9c69c16"
